collection of my vim configuration options and plugins in Ubuntu

Add the vimrc.local in /etc/vim folder

Add doc, ftplugin, nerdtree_plugin, plugin and syntax folders in yout $HOME/.vim folder.
e.g.
/home/lfrsilva/.vim/doc
/home/lfrsilva/.vim/ftplugin
/home/lfrsilva/.vim/nerdtree_plugin
/home/lfrsilva/.vim/plugin
/home/lfrsilva/.vim/syntax
